<div style=" float: center;margin: auto;text-align: middle; padding: 2px 5px 2px 2px; color: black; background-color: white; border-radius: 8px;">
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em>献给读者-III</em></p>
</div>
<hr />
<p><br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<div class="content-panel standalone" style="font-family: Courier New, Courier, monospace; width: auto; padding: 10px 30px; margin: 20px auto; background: url(http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/about-the-scp-foundation/bg-marble.png) repeat; text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.25)">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong>英雄陨落，梦呓牵肠。</strong><br />
<strong>今生此处，来世何方？</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong>彼岸中转，魂恋心伤。</strong><br />
<strong>落魄之人，殒命何方？</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong>怨世俗语，当是飞网。</strong><br />
<strong>危阑休倚，路在何方？</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong>困情之人，知情何物？</strong><br />
<strong>怅望花海，冥河荡漾。</strong><br /></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
