<br />
<br />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">这之后的故事……</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>完全不给你思考的时间，耳畔已经传来沉重的脚步声。你知道它们是来找你的，也知道它们和你一样目标明确。</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>你快速地向声音反方向跑去，对于这里的地形你已铭记在心。</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>脚步声越发密集，也越来越逼近。你拉倒了身边的书架，企图阻挡它们。</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>记忆中的道路发生了改变，越来越多错位的书架出现在身边。有楼梯通往楼上和楼下，甚至还有横倒的楼梯——可这里只有一层，也没有所谓楼梯。</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong></p>
</div>
<br />
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-d4ae3c3743703b214accef6761ed55e5" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>P162</em></a></li>
</ul>
<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<div style=" float: center;margin: auto;text-align: middle; padding: 2px 5px 2px 2px; color: black; background-color: white; border-radius: 8px;">
<p><em>埃舍尔效应</em></p>
<hr />
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/local--files/dr-beyondawn-s-personal-page/paradox" alt="paradox" class="image" /></div>
<hr />
<p>P162</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
//<![CDATA[
OZONE.dom.onDomReady(function(){
