<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p>仿徨与无助。腿渐渐无力，眼前开始模糊。跌倒之前，你注意到了这片浩浩荡荡的花海。</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p><em>至少……摆脱它们了。</em>你再次翻开书页。</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>.</strong><br />
<strong>.</strong></p>
</div>
<br />
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
